item.title: Super fan
item.description: SO my friend ella finally finished her website. It is pretty good. I like it. I am proud of her. check it out here. it is in chinese. so good luck. today I weird. I am tired. but full of energy. so many friends are visiting and hanging out. it is weird that it is all happening now. but.. yea know.. this is edgy - this is interesting.
